Package com.brightcove.plugin.onceux.event

Class Summary
AdDataReadyEventHandler Provide a class to deal with the completion of ad server processing, when the content can begin being played.
EndAdBreakEventHandler Provide a class to deal with the completion of an ad break.
LearnMoreClickHandler Provide a class to deal with User clicks on the "Learn More" button as part of processing the <VideoClicks> element.
OnceUxEventListener Provide a base class for all OnceUX event handlers.

ProgressEventHandler Provide a class to handle an SDK progress event.
SendImpressionEventHandler Provide a class to send an event corresponding to a <Impression> element.
SendTrackingBeaconEventHandler Provide a class to send out a tracking beacon as part of processing for the <Tracking> elements encountered in an ad break.
StartAdBreakEventHandler Provide a class to deal with the start of an ad break.
